window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The official novelization of the brand new</b> <b>game</b></p> <p>His vengeance against the gods of Olympus years behind him, Kratos now lives as a man in the realm of Norse gods and monsters. It is in this harsh, unforgiving world that he must fight to survive...and teach his son to do the same.&nbsp;</p> <p>This startling reimagining of <i>God of War</i> deconstructs the core elements that defined the series - satisfying combat, breathtaking scale, and a powerful narrative - and fuses them anew.</p>"; 
